      "writtenOn": "2018-01-20T02:23:29Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "What is unnecessary? You\u0027re saying \"UNIQUE (name, host_id)\" is unnecessary because \"UNIQUE (name, host_id)\" covers it. They\u0027re the same. I don\u0027t understand.",
      "parentUuid": "97db2359_df981e9f",
